subject: Basketball
College Athletics
Basketball (College)
lead_paragraph: Zack Rosen had 28 points and 5 assists as Pennsylvania (11-9, 3-0 Ivy league) beat visiting Princeton (10-9, 1-2) by 82-67, ending a five-game losing streak in the series.
